{"tid":2513121,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日北韓......明日香港！","createTime":"2021-05-02T09:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T04:56:52.000Z","uid":193220,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10f8bd7b00591005ba5363c37c907da4ca12a6f3","tid":2513121,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"港共柒婆見到北韓對學生偷睇韓劇大懲罰<br />\n已經即刻打晒飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一步遲早立法禁止<br />\n香港人聽KPOP JPOP 英文歌<br />\n香港人睇韓劇/日劇/台劇/美劇<br />\n<br />\n柒婆最鍾意政治正確<br />\n支那同日本關係開始轉差<br />\n泡菜仔反支那氣氛越嚟越勁<br />\n台灣同支那關係會點大家都知<br />\n美國仲繼續制裁柒婆<br />\n<br />\n見BTS 親美唔親支那<br />\n好勝心強柒婆肯定最仇恨 BTS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲早柒婆一定會立法巜港區反動思想文化排斥法》<br />\n目的就要限制西方國家或者韓國日本外國勢力文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時立法會一定全體表決通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n虐待狂柒婆要你香港人生活仲慘過大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6037d0591713ee3d788a469bec96c7f3abe66916","tid":2513121,"uid":11858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7dd53aa7f053e2517fe9ee0b829f172e9d2614","tid":2513121,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"所以有得走就真係好快d走，8月前仲唔走就無機會，到時入集中營唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b252079f365c0c203354236ef63efd335d6e5a","tid":2513121,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"韓國人仲要本身好撐香港人示威<br />\n柒婆見到唔嬲至奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本人就唔知啦"},{"pid":"dfb55c17a1b9b20568abc8abf21879739e5bcb5e","tid":2513121,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff7dd53aa7f053e2517fe9ee0b829f172e9d2614","ti